# Phase 0 runs entirely on an in-memory mock client (src/api/client.ts), so no
# backend URL is required to run the shell, Storybook, or the tests.
#
# These are placeholders for a later phase that points the typed Tessera data
# client at the real .NET broker read-model. The portal never bakes secrets:
# OIDC sign-in (Microsoft /common) and short-TTL handles come from the broker.
VITE_TESSERA_API_URL=/tessera-api
